cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "charmmgui2cp2k: automated CHARMM-GUI/AMBER to CP2K QM/MM input generator"
abstract: >-
  A terminal-native wizard (CLI and Textual TUI) that converts CHARMM-GUI
  QM/MM Interfacer / AMBER biomolecular setups into validated, immediately
  runnable CP2K QM/MM input files, with automated link-atom handling,
  boundary charge redistribution, spin-state risk analysis, and CP2K
  version-capability gating.
type: software
authors:
